1. Moj *razmišljao* je da li da ode na putovanje ili ostane kod kuće. (My thinking was whether to go on a trip or stay at home.)
2. Kada se baviš poslom koji voliš, tvoje *razmišljanje* postaje kreativnije. (When you're doing a job you love, your thinking becomes more creative.)
3. Često *razmišljam* o prošlosti i razmišljam o tome šta sam mogao da uradim drugačije. (I often think about the past and think about what I could have done differently.)
4. Novinari su pozvali direktora na konferenciju kako bi dobili odgovore na neka *razmišljanja*. (Journalists called the director to a conference to get answers to some thoughts.)
5. Moje *razmišljanje* se promenilo nakon što sam pročitao taj članak. (My thinking changed after I read that article.)
6. Deca bi trebalo da budu podstaknuta da razvijaju kritičko *razmišljanje*. (Children should be encouraged to develop critical thinking.)
7. Moje *razmišljanje* je da se fokusiram na svoje ciljeve i ne gubim vreme na nevažne stvari. (My thinking is to focus on my goals and not waste time on unimportant things.)
8. Neki ljudi se bave duhovnim *razmišljanjem* kako bi pronašli smisao života. (Some people engage in spiritual thinking to find meaning in life.)